  "img": "systems/pf1/icons/skills/blue_06.jpg",
  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>This character can avoid damage from many area-effect attacks. If she makes a successful <a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/gamemastering/combat#TOC-Reflex\">Reflex</a>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/gamemastering/combat#TOC-Saving-Throws\">saving throw</a> against an attack that normally deals half damage on a successful save, she instead takes no damage. Evasion can be used only if the character is wearing light armor or no armor. A <a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/gamemastering/conditions#TOC-Helpless\">helpless</a> character does not gain the benefit of <a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/classes/core-classes/rogue#TOC-Evasion-Ex-\">evasion</a>.</p>"
    },
